attributes.Long form description: The student is disassembling a black IKEA Rashult table. He disassembles the wheels, then the bolts holding on the three trays, and finally the side bars.

attributes.Transcription: Hello. Welcome to our study. Thank you for agreeing to take part. In front of you, you will see a bathroom cabinet from IKEA.
Your task for now will be to please disassemble it.

attributes.Action sentence: The student disassembles the first wheel from the base frame.
The student disassembles the second wheel from the base frame.
The student disassembles  the third wheel from the base frame.
The student disassembles the fourth wheel from the base frame.
The student disassembles the first bolt from the middle tray.

attributes.Action Correctness: Wrong Action, corrected by instructor verbally

attributes.Action Correctness: Wrong Action, corrected by instructor verbally

attributes.Transcription:
While you are screwing the middle shelf, while you are screwing just hold the grip on the other side. 
Make sure it doesn't rotate.

attributes.Transcription: Thank you very much. That was everything for this task.
You may now press stop button.
